WEBVTT

00:00:00.486 --> 00:00:03.455
Danas bih želio razgovarati

00:00:03.455 --> 00:00:04.812
o jednoj od mojih najdražih tema,

00:00:04.812 --> 00:00:08.264
a to je neuroznanost spavanja.

00:00:08.264 --> 00:00:11.348
Postoji zvuk --

00:00:11.348 --> 00:00:13.228
(Budilica) --

00:00:13.228 --> 00:00:15.340
aah, radi --

00:00:15.340 --> 00:00:18.923
zvuk koji nam je očajnički svima dobro poznat,

00:00:18.923 --> 00:00:21.109
naravno, to je zvuk budilice.

00:00:21.109 --> 00:00:24.168
Ono što radi taj grozni, sablasni zvuk je

00:00:24.168 --> 00:00:29.555
da zaustavlja jedno od najvažnijih iskustava

00:00:29.555 --> 00:00:32.732
koje imamo, a to je spavanje.